description: This visualisation provides estimates for the diameter of the right of way distances that may be applied to the 500kV high voltage direct connection line running from Moyale to Suswa. The minimum distance of 30 Meters is  applied up to an approximate maximum of 65 Meters as per the  standards set by KETRACO.
